        The constructor of the class. All parameters must be initialized, so passed as parameters.
        Parameters:
        player - The name of the player who made the move.
        tokens - The updated number of tokens.
        grid - The updated grid.
        draftPool - The array containing the dice in the updated DraftPool.
        roundTrack - The current RoundTrack.
        forcedSelection - The index of the die in draftPool that must be used by the player.
